HEADWORD: automate
<hw>automate</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>make automatic; to
change [a process] so that it is mostly automatic; to substitute
machinery for human labor in an activity.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> automatize.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]  [<source>+PJC</source>]</p>

